    "The 'Risk Chain Mapping' component of the landscape assessment has been omitted from this public report in line with our responsible disclosure commitments.",
    "The 'tool assessment' consisted of two components: evaluating misuse-relevant capabilities against multiple scenarios and assessing the maturity and availability of each tool.",
    "Together, these components were combined into a composite 'Red', 'Amber' or 'Green' score for each tool.",
    "For full methodological details, see Appendix A.",
